WEBVTT

00:00:01.188 --> 00:00:04.659
mir hobn geredt vegn antisemitizm in ayer shtot.

00:00:04.850 --> 00:00:08.805
yetst. vegn antisemitizm vel ikh aykh ibergebn yetst

00:00:08.805 --> 00:00:12.354
a zakh vos ikh hob es mitgemakht, vos ikh hob dos getun.

00:00:13.727 --> 00:00:16.196
vegn vos handlt zikh? ikh bin geganen in shul arayn,

00:00:16.224 --> 00:00:17.822
ikh bin aheymgekumen fun di shule,

00:00:17.912 --> 00:00:19.982
dos iz gevezn nokh far di milkhome.

00:00:22.586 --> 00:00:24.656
ikh bin aheymgekumen tsvelef a zeyger,

00:00:24.813 --> 00:00:26.579
bin ikh arayngekumen in gevelb arayn,

00:00:26.889 --> 00:00:31.389
ze ikh vi mayn mame zitst, in droysn farn gevelb shteyen tsvey shkotsim,

00:00:31.968 --> 00:00:34.359
un me shrayt "NIE KUPUJ OD ZYDOW.

00:00:35.259 --> 00:00:36.823
NIE KUPUJ OD ZYDOW."

00:00:37.368 --> 00:00:38.291
dos meynt?

00:00:38.176 --> 00:00:43.539
dos heyst, nisht tsu koyfn bay keyn yidn, nisht koyfn bay yidn, nisht arayngeyn tsu yidn.

00:00:44.118 --> 00:00:47.319
un me halt in eyn shrayen, me shteyt in der FRONT, far undzer gevelb.

00:00:48.287 --> 00:00:49.901
gey ikh arayn in gevelb arayn,

00:00:50.075 --> 00:00:52.229
zog ikh tsu di mamen, zog ikh, "vos geyt do tsu?"

00:00:52.961 --> 00:00:54.609
mayn mame zogt, "Pinekl,

00:00:56.673 --> 00:00:59.030
zey veln mid veln zey avekgeyn.

00:00:59.525 --> 00:01:01.882
zoln zey shrayen, zey veln dokh mid vern."

00:01:02.512 --> 00:01:04.548
zog ikh, "oyf dem vartstu, zey zoln mid vern?

00:01:05.651 --> 00:01:09.341
un az zey veln shrayen biz far nakht?" "iz farfaln, veln zey shrayen biz far nakht."

00:01:11.203 --> 00:01:14.100
heyb ikh zikh oyf, un tu zikh oys mayn tash,

00:01:14.595 --> 00:01:17.543
vos ikh hob gehat lign mayne ale bikher fun di shul,

00:01:18.459 --> 00:01:19.955
un leyg es avek,

00:01:20.349 --> 00:01:23.417
un mir hobn gehat aza hinter gevelb, fun hintn,

00:01:23.420 --> 00:01:27.088
un me hot gehat farshidene skhoyres, ir veyst di groyse skhoyres, peklekh,

00:01:27.088 --> 00:01:28.528
kestlekh,

00:01:29.613 --> 00:01:34.282
hob ikh aruntergegangen dortn un dortn hob ikh gehat dortn an ayzernem shtekele,

00:01:34.507 --> 00:01:38.434
a lang ayzernem shtekl. a shtik fun ayzn.

00:01:39.198 --> 00:01:41.994
ikh hob dos tsu mir genumen, ikh hob dos genumen in di zayt,

00:01:42.219 --> 00:01:45.841
un mit dem shtekele bin ikh aroysgegangen tsurik fun droysn di FRONT.

00:01:46.691 --> 00:01:49.098
ikh hob genumen dem ayzernem shtekn,

00:01:49.543 --> 00:01:53.402
ikh hob derlangt eynem oyfn kop, un tsveytn oyfn kop.

00:01:53.492 --> 00:01:55.106
un beyde hobn zikh oysgetsoygn.

00:01:56.040 --> 00:01:57.503
un se gist zikh di blutn.

00:01:58.250 --> 00:01:59.814
un se vert a geshrey,

00:01:59.988 --> 00:02:02.632
"a yid hot geharget tsvey goyim, tsvey shkotsim."

00:02:03.819 --> 00:02:05.332
un a tsuzamenloyf,

00:02:06.333 --> 00:02:08.808
un gantse nakht iz geven dray POLICE,

00:02:09.100 --> 00:02:12.757
iz geven eyner a POLICEMAN, zeyer a sharfer, hot men gerufn, dos iz der vayser kop.

00:02:13.303 --> 00:02:15.620
er hot nisht gehat keyn hor, hot men gerufn dos iz der vayser kop.

00:02:15.620 --> 00:02:18.765
er iz gekumen. er iz ongekumen,

00:02:19.310 --> 00:02:20.857
hot er gezen vos tut zikh,

00:02:21.318 --> 00:02:25.666
hot er bald gelozt rufn a CAR, me zol di tsvey mentshn avekfirn in HOSPITAL arayn.

00:02:26.516 --> 00:02:29.447
un vi er hot zey oyfgeshtelt, er hot zey a bisl arumgevisht,

00:02:29.638 --> 00:02:33.699
zogt er, dreyts enk oys un gibts a kuk vi ikh shtey mitn shtekele in der hant.

00:02:34.025 --> 00:02:36.500
nisht antlofn, ikh bin geshtanen oyfn plats.

00:02:37.265 --> 00:02:44.111
zogt er tsu zey, tsu di tsvey, "ze ver es hot enk dos getun. ikh vil eyder ikh fir aykh avek, zolt ir kukn ver es hot dos getun."

00:02:44.370 --> 00:02:46.744
THIS BOYtshikl hot aykh getun.

00:02:47.306 --> 00:02:50.135
