00:02:50.900 --> 00:02:57.259
"se vet nisht zayn," zogt er, "keyn groyser mentsh un an alter mentshn un a gezunter mentsh, zol aykh dos tun. a kind ken aykh oykh dos tun.

00:02:57.262 --> 00:02:58.539
un dos iz dos kind."

00:02:59.928 --> 00:03:01.559
vi alt zent ir geven demolts?

00:03:01.565 --> 00:03:02.296
ver?

00:03:02.207 --> 00:03:02.910
ir.

00:03:02.882 --> 00:03:04.803
ikh bin alt geven demolts elef yor.

00:03:04.803 --> 00:03:06.336
efsher ariber elef yor.

00:03:06.645 --> 00:03:08.867
far der milkhome, kurts far der milkhome.

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:13.508
un me hot zey avekgefirt in shpitol arayn, me hot bandazhirt zey di kep,

00:03:14.407 --> 00:03:18.269
un s- un mayn mame rayst zikh barn kop, vos hostu dos getun?

00:03:18.269 --> 00:03:19.903
