00:03:28.042 --> 00:03:31.884
"bist a khevreman, gey yetst arayn, bist gekumen fun SCHOOL un gey es epes.

00:03:32.261 --> 00:03:33.723
host gemakht a gutn JOB."

00:03:35.467 --> 00:03:38.111
dos iz geven der politsey? der politsey man?

00:03:36.902 --> 00:03:42.029
