"du host gemakht vos host badorfn makhn."

00:03:44.175 --> 00:03:46.380
hob ikh nokh gefregt dem politsyant,

00:03:46.537 --> 00:03:47.662
zog ikh, "zog nor,

00:03:47.820 --> 00:03:51.645
mir tsoln genug," zog ikh, "misim, podatkes,

00:03:52.055 --> 00:03:54.919
