00:04:02.282 --> 00:04:03.812
un dos vos ikh hob getun."

00:04:04.307 --> 00:04:05.499
"host gut getun."

00:04:05.555 --> 00:04:07.220
er hot mir gedankt, er hot mir gegebn di hant,

00:04:07.293 --> 00:04:09.619
ikh bin arayngeganen un mayn mame hot zikh baruikt,

00:04:09.619 --> 00:04:14.932
zi hot gezen vos ikh hob getun, zi iz geven tsufridn me hot eynem avekgefirt un ikh bin shoyn fertik, un dos vos ikh hob gemakht.

00:04:15.748 --> 00:04:19.185
eyn zakh ken ikh nor zogn, ikh bin geboyrn gevorn aza min UNK,

00:04:20.625 --> 00:04:23.640
mayne ale brider zenen gevezn shvakhe,

00:04:23.814 --> 00:04:26.137
zey hobn dos, keyner hot dos nisht gekont dos tun,

00:04:26.750 --> 00:04:29.026
un un mikh fun kleynvayz oyf,

00:04:29.026 --> 00:04:32.561
