00:05:19.181 --> 00:05:23.732
vifl mol hob ikh gekont brengen? ikh hob dokh gehat, f- fir brider, finef brider, finef brider hob ikh gehat,

00:05:24.513 --> 00:05:28.507
un di shvestern, yeder eyner iz mit mir gegangen, un di mame, di tate iz nisht gegangen mit mir,

00:05:28.631 --> 00:05:30.262
keyn mol nisht. er iz nisht gegangen.

00:05:31.550 --> 00:05:36.793
un SO ikh hob shoyn nisht gehat ver se zol mir, zol mir sheyn brengen tsu di SCHOOL arayn. iz tsu morgns bin ikh gegangen iz shoyn geven gut.

00:05:37.052 --> 00:05:42.362
ober tsum sof hot zikh aroysgevizn az der gantser PRINCIPAL, se gekumen der driter may, me hot gedorfn geyn makhn,

00:05:42.452 --> 00:05:44.424
aroysgeyn, makhn oyf a marsh,

00:05:44.443 --> 00:05:47.131
gegn gegn, dem, gegn dem,

00:05:47.131 --> 00:05:48.675
MAYOR fun di CITY,

00:05:48.695 --> 00:05:51.156
dritn MAY iz geven shtendik a yontev in Poyln,

00:05:51.193 --> 00:05:52.993
nisht in ershtn MAY, in dritn MAY.

00:05:53.572 --> 00:05:57.493
ho'mir marshirt fun ale SCHOOLn, hot er mikh oysgelernt vi azoy ikh zol makhn, ikh zol makhn, ikh zol kukn

00:05:57.493 --> 00:06:01.644
un salutirn farn farn far dem MAYOR fun di shtot,

00:06:01.644 --> 00:06:02.949
hot er mikh genumen.

00:06:03.107 --> 00:06:05.295
er hot dokh azoy fil goyishe, hot er mikh genumen.

00:06:05.688 --> 00:06:07.927
mikh hor gehaltn UNK du bist a khevreman.

00:06:08.068 --> 00:06:09.227
du kenst dos tun.

00:06:09.671 --> 00:06:13.192
un in di shules vos ir zent gegangen iz gevezn gemisht.

