se forgekumen geshlegn, ober ikh hob zey, ikh hob zey ale ge- ikh hob ale opge- ale genumen nekome in zey, ale tseklapt.

00:06:38.229 --> 00:06:40.446
shpeter hobn zey oyfgehert. zey hobn moyre gehat.

00:06:40.805 --> 00:06:43.888
zey zenen gekumen, khotsh ikh hob gekont shlogn a gresern sheygets.

00:06:44.315 --> 00:06:45.761
zey zenen ale antlofn far mir.

00:06:46.425 --> 00:06:50.874
zenen geven oykh azelkhe yinglekh, yidishe yinglekh vi ir, vos hot oykh,

00:06:49.884 --> 00:06:53.737
kimat kimat vi nisht, ikh bin geve- me hot nor gevolt kumen rufn oyf Pinekn, "Pinek,

00:06:53.737 --> 00:06:55.734
kum me hot mikh geshlogn!" "ver hot dikh geshlogn?"

00:06:55.875 --> 00:06:57.692
hot men gevizn hob ikh im bald tseklapt.

00:07:01.629 --> 00:07:06.534
