00:07:06.978 --> 00:07:08.609
fun oysland?

00:07:09.037 --> 00:07:12.879
se hot zikh dernentert tsu der milkhome, hot men nisht mer gehert vi di polyakn hobn geshrign,

00:07:13.323 --> 00:07:15.058
"Hitler PRZYJDZIE UNK."

