00:07:26.233 --> 00:07:28.978
hobn hobn zey gevolt a milkhome?

00:07:29.152 --> 00:07:32.538
nisht vos zey hobn gevolt. zey hobn gevolt, zey hobn ge- zey hobn gevust vos zey viln.

00:07:29.169 --> 00:07:30.665
UNK

00:07:32.628 --> 00:07:36.099
