00:07:36.307 --> 00:07:37.634
undz vet men erleydikn.

00:07:37.708 --> 00:07:40.976
zey hobn gevust az di daytshn hasn di yidn,

00:07:41.100 --> 00:07:44.267
un zey shlogn di yidn, azoy az

00:07:44.576 --> 00:07:47.625
