00:07:47.883 --> 00:07:49.329
dos vos zey hobn gehoft.

00:07:50.162 --> 00:07:52.671
tsi zey vet zayn shlekht, dos hobn zey nisht getrakht.

00:07:52.997 --> 00:07:58.121
tsi di daytshn veln hargenen goyim oykh, dos hobn zey nisht getrakht, zey hobn nor getrakht az di daytshn darfn hargenen yidn.

00:07:58.211 --> 00:07:59.471
