00:08:31.131 --> 00:08:35.127
az ikh bin antlofn fun a lager, ikh hob gedarfn a por dolar, ikh bin aheymgekumen tsu mayn shtot,

00:08:35.402 --> 00:08:42.564
un ikh hob badorfn ibernekhtikn di zelbe nakht, se geven a vinter, bi- bin arayngekumen bay vemenen? se nisht geven keyn yidn. bay a goy bin ikh arayngekumen,

00:08:42.564 --> 00:08:48.040
