00:09:01.728 --> 00:09:07.257
ikh bin geven tsufridn er lozt mikh geyn. vayl mayn's a khaver iz gegangen kumen mit mir, un er iz gegangen tsu zayns a goy, hot men im derharget.

00:09:08.141 --> 00:09:10.197
ober far der milkhome,

00:09:10.197 --> 00:09:13.367
di di hige bafelkerung, di nisht yidishe bafelkerung,

00:09:13.490 --> 00:09:16.694
