00:09:16.694 --> 00:09:20.336
mit frayndshaft tsu yidn un gegn antisemitizm?

00:09:20.578 --> 00:09:23.154
se nisht geven azelkhes. dos gedenk ikh nisht.

00:09:23.430 --> 00:09:26.684
