demolts bin ikh alt gevezn bald tsvelef yor.

00:10:59.567 --> 00:11:01.468
gedenk ir vu ir zent gevezn?

00:11:02.317 --> 00:11:06.075
ikh gedenk azoy fil azoy vi yetst, vi di daytshn zenen arayngekumen tsu undz in di shtot.

00:11:07.650 --> 00:11:09.011
ikh bin gevezn a yingele,

00:11:09.506 --> 00:11:12.622
un ikh hob gevolt zen di daytshn. ikh hob nisht gevust vos heyst a daytsh,

00:11:13.691 --> 00:11:17.803
vos hob ikh gevust vos daytshn zenen vos hob ikh gevust vos di amerikaner zenen, englender zenen?

00:11:17.910 --> 00:11:19.288
ikh hob UNK di daytshn.

00:11:19.563 --> 00:11:23.692
bin ikh aroysgegangen a bisele indroysn aroyskukn, hob ikh gezen me flit adurkh oyf mototsiklen.

00:11:25.436 --> 00:11:27.484
hob ikh vider aroysgekukt, vayter do.

00:11:27.484 --> 00:11:29.599
biz hob ikh mikh gegebn a ruk aroys,

00:11:29.705 --> 00:11:31.421
shoyn in droysn oyf di gas,

00:11:31.697 --> 00:11:36.855
hobn zey mikh a derze gegebn, hobn a zey a shray gegebn, "HALT!" un mitn biks tsu mir, ikh hob shoyn nisht gekent antloyfn.

00:11:37.316 --> 00:11:38.492
bin ikh geblibn shteyn.

00:11:38.598 --> 00:11:39.892
dos vos ikh gedenk.

00:11:40.083 --> 00:11:41.967
di daytsh iz tsugekumen, hot mikh genumen.

00:11:42.193 --> 00:11:47.143
er hot undz avekgefirt oyf a gas, un di ale, di pakhdonim, vos zenen arayngekumen in di shtot arayn, hobn gekhapt azelkhe

00:11:47.143 --> 00:11:50.861
mentshn, eyntsele, un me hot zey ale avekgefirt oyf eyn plats, mikh oykhet.

00:11:51.018 --> 00:11:52.244
ikh bin geven a kind,

00:11:52.301 --> 00:11:53.749
me hot yedern bazukht,

00:11:53.769 --> 00:11:56.632
bakukt, vos me hot, ven me hot, vos me hot,

00:11:56.739 --> 00:11:59.867
un me hot gornisht gehat, hot men geheysn me zol aheymgeyn.

00:11:59.878 --> 00:12:03.872
un demolts hot men iz, mayn mame hot shoyn geveynt, in ge⟨trern⟩ me hot mikh, me hot mikh shoyn farkhapt.

00:12:04.282 --> 00:12:07.432
dos iz geven der ershter minut,` baym aray- ven zey hobn farnumen di shtot.

00:12:07.573 --> 00:12:12.579
oder me hot mikh opgelozt, un ikh bin aheymgegangen. ikh bin aheymgekumen, "vos iz mit dir geshen?" "ikh hob aroysgekukt, er hot mikh farkhapt."

00:12:12.770 --> 00:12:15.262
me hot a leyg gegebn di biks tsu mir, vos hob ikh gezolt tun?

00:12:15.605 --> 00:12:17.439
hob ikh gevart, me iz gekumen, me hot mikh genumen.

00:12:17.917 --> 00:12:22.771
un eyder di daytshn zenen arayngegangen, iz geven dortn epes a bombardirn,?

00:12:22.794 --> 00:12:30.399
se gevezn, avade. eyder zey zenen arayngekumen zikher iz gevezn, di shiseray, bombardirungen, OH YEA! ober di zelbe nakht vi zey hobn farnumen di shtot

00:12:30.658 --> 00:12:40.187
vayzt zikh oys az se hot emetser aroys- geven a groyser mark, a tsenter, der mark in di shtot in Apt iz geven a groyser mark, un arum un arum iz geven groyse gesheftn, mayn shvester hot dort gehat a groys gesheft,

00:12:40.428 --> 00:12:43.527
di raykhste gesheftn zenen geven dortn arum un arum in mark, groys gesheftn,

00:12:44.343 --> 00:12:47.577
vayzt zikh oys az se hot emetser gemuzt shisn dort oyf a patrol,

00:12:47.870 --> 00:12:53.824
hot men farbrent, in dem zelbn nakht iz geven a shiseray a gantse nakht, mentshn hobn nisht gekent der nakht tsumakhn keyn oyg.

00:12:53.824 --> 00:12:56.640
me iz ofn gevezn, me shist, az se geven geferlekh.

00:12:56.848 --> 00:13:01.857
me hot azoy lang geshosn un geklapt un bombes, hot men farbrent dortn dray groyse hayzer in dem mark.

00:13:01.857 --> 00:13:05.342
se hot vayzt zikh oys emetser geshosn oyf a patrol, hot men farbrent dray hayzer,

00:13:05.370 --> 00:13:07.288
mit di mentshn, mit alem. farbrent.

00:13:07.412 --> 00:13:10.309
ver se hot gekent antloyfn iz antlofn, ver se iz nisht antlofn iz farbrent gevorn.

00:13:11.208 --> 00:13:14.982
un fun ayere brider, fun ayer familyes, emetser hot gevezn in militer demolts?

00:13:15.798 --> 00:13:17.711
eyn bruder iz gevezn in militer.

00:13:17.711 --> 00:13:18.560
Khaim.

00:13:19.545 --> 00:13:21.483
ir hot gehert fun imen?

00:13:21.401 --> 00:13:27.707
OH YEA! YEA. er iz geven in militer, in der poylisher armey, vos me hot im arayngenumen in di milkhome arayn,

00:13:21.483 --> 00:13:23.151
der vos iz geven in militer?

00:13:27.881 --> 00:13:33.191
ober er hot zikh bafrayt, un er iz aheymgekumen, er hot nisht gevoynt bay undz in di shtot, er hot gevoynt in Skazhisk.

00:13:34.496 --> 00:13:42.692
Khaim, der vos iz geven in militer, er iz geven der eyntsiker in der milkhome, vos er iz, vos di polyakn, vos der poylisher armey, hot im arayngenumen in der milkhome arayn AGAINST di daytshn.

00:13:42.984 --> 00:13:45.881
ober er hot zikh bafrayt. er iz geven ober oyfn front...

00:13:47.000 --> 00:13:48.716
un er iz tsurikgekumen aheym?

00:13:48.435 --> 00:13:51.062
er iz tsurikgekumen aheym. tsu zayn froy un kind.

00:13:52.552 --> 00:13:54.031
iz er geven in plen?

00:13:54.122 --> 00:13:55.196
er iz nisht geven plen.

00:13:56.248 --> 00:14:03.003
er hot zikh oys- er hot zikh ibergetsoygn, er hot oysgetun di malbushim, un er hot oysgetun di kleyder, er iz geven bay a, dortn bay a goy, er hot oysgetun di kleyder, er hot ibergegebn ales,

00:14:03.048 --> 00:14:04.544
un er iz aheymgekumen tsurik.

00:14:06.339 --> 00:14:11.210
akhuts dem intsident vos ir hot dertseylt frier vegn di daytshn vos hobn aykh

00:14:11.537 --> 00:14:12.934
farhaltn,

00:14:12.228 --> 00:14:12.982
ye.

00:14:12.934 --> 00:14:17.454
gedenkt ir di okupirter armey vi azoy zey hobn zikh oysge- oyfgefirt?

00:14:17.274 --> 00:14:22.044
bald dem ershtn tog, azoy ikh hob aykh gezogt, di zelbe nakht iz geven di sreyfe vos me hot farbrent a por hayzer,

00:14:22.252 --> 00:14:25.014
shpeter iz gevezn, az me zogt, se gegangen

00:14:25.509 --> 00:14:34.380
ni- in di BEGINNING iz geven gants guter BUSINESS, zenen arayngekumen di daytshn in gevelb arayn, zey hobn gekoyft, zey hobn gehat tsu leyzn, zey hobn ge- zey hobn ge- nisht getsolt mit keyn poylish gelt, zey hobn getsolt mit mark.

00:14:34.470 --> 00:14:43.917
un der mark iz vert geven mer vi der, vi der zlote, azoy az me hot gemakht guter BUSINESS, in der BEGINNING hot zikh nisht aroysgevizn oyf azoy vayt vos di daytshn vet undz optun.

00:14:43.917 --> 00:14:49.157
me hot gevust az zey zenen antisemitn, mir ho'mir gevust di Hitler, ober az dos armey zol konen dos bavayzn,

00:14:49.157 --> 00:14:51.873
hobn zikh bavizn zeyer orntlekh, zeyer fayn,

00:14:51.873 --> 00:14:52.810
in der BEGINNING.

00:14:52.810 --> 00:14:57.381
mentshn hobn gemakht BUSINESS, me hot gehandlt, me hot gekoyft, un zey hobn opgekoyft, zey hobn aheymgeshikt peklekh,

00:14:57.555 --> 00:14:59.054
se iz gegangen zeyer fayn.

00:14:59.057 --> 00:15:02.631
se iz azoy tsugegangen bizkele fertsikstn yor.

00:15:02.631 --> 00:15:04.839
in fertsikstn yor hot zikh ongehoybn di tsores.

00:15:04.862 --> 00:15:09.733
vi lang hot genumen di daytshn araynkumen nokh dem vi der milkhome hot oysgebrokhn?

00:15:09.992 --> 00:15:11.187
vi lang se hot genumen?

00:15:11.207 --> 00:15:14.967
der milkhome hot oysgebrokhn, ikh veys, me iz arayngekumen tsu undz in shtot arayn iz gevezn efsher

00:15:14.967 --> 00:15:15.993
akht, tsen tog.

00:15:17.096 --> 00:15:18.930
nokh dem vi der milkhome hot oysgebrokhn.

00:15:17.990 --> 00:15:18.879
oysgebrokhn.

00:15:21.298 --> 00:15:26.034
in di okupirter daytshisher armey hot ayngefirt vos in shtot bay aykh?

00:15:26.597 --> 00:15:30.051
zey hobn gehat politsey? zey hobn gehat GENDARMERIE?

00:15:28.233 --> 00:15:29.527
zey hobn GENDARMERIE.

00:15:29.735 --> 00:15:39.703
zey hobn gehat di GENDARMERIE, ober hob ikh aykh gezogt in der BEGINNING, di ershte por khadoshim, hot men nisht gefilt gornisht; me hot gemakht gute BUSINESS un mentshn hobn gearbet, me hot gefirt BUSINESS, un me hot alts getun.

00:15:39.776 --> 00:15:43.292
hot men gezogt, "se undz gornisht azoy shlekht", der, dervayl zet men

00:15:43.292 --> 00:15:46.621
nisht keyn diferents, se gevezn zeyer fayn.

00:15:46.728 --> 00:15:54.215
ober se hot zikh aroysgevizn nisht lang, a por khadoshim, biz se gekumen di nayntsn fertsik, demolts hot zikh ongehoybn zikh di tsores oyf azoy vayt

00:15:54.272 --> 00:15:56.241
az se gornisht geven ibertsugreyfn.

00:15:56.668 --> 00:15:59.312
un di yidisher bafelkerung in ayer shtot

00:16:00.515 --> 00:16:05.522
zenen ammerstns geblibn, tsi a sakh zenen antlofn?

00:16:05.898 --> 00:16:08.941
se nisht antlofn keyn mentshn, ober vos iz?

00:16:08.941 --> 00:16:11.326
zey hobn ongehoybn tsu antloyfn shpeter.

00:16:11.720 --> 00:16:14.215
se hot zikh ongehoybn vern erger, erger, erger,

00:16:14.215 --> 00:16:17.503
ts- tsum vinter tsu, bay farn vinter hot ongehoybn tsu vern erger,

00:16:17.812 --> 00:16:22.008
iz mayn's a bruder, YISRAEL, er iz antlofn keyn Rusland.

00:16:22.385 --> 00:16:23.493
zogt mayn fo-

00:16:22.588 --> 00:16:23.915
ven iz dos gevezn?

00:16:26.098 --> 00:16:29.974
dos iz gevezn nokh di yomtoyvim, dos heyst azoy nokh sukes.

00:16:29.760 --> 00:16:30.666
in vos a yor?

00:16:31.937 --> 00:16:33.973
in nayntsn nayn un draysik.

00:16:35.868 --> 00:16:38.414
hot er gezogt az er fort avek.

00:16:38.417 --> 00:16:41.466
zogt mayn foter, ikh gedenk gut vi haynt, er vil gelt.

00:16:42.838 --> 00:16:43.907
du vilst gelt?

00:16:43.907 --> 00:16:47.861
OKAY, mayn foter hot im gegebn gelt, "vu forstu?" zogt er er fort avek keyn Rusland.

00:16:48.795 --> 00:16:51.709
keyn Rusland? er vil do nisht zitsn.

00:16:52.558 --> 00:16:56.332
er zet az se vart oyf undz zeyer biterer tsaytn.

00:16:57.165 --> 00:16:59.539
un er zet me vet nisht kenen do lebn.

00:17:00.303 --> 00:17:02.086
di daytshn zenen yetst do.

00:17:02.312 --> 00:17:04.570
un se vart oyf undz a groyser mageyfe.

00:17:04.572 --> 00:17:06.085
er vil nisht blaybn.

00:17:07.138 --> 00:17:08.738
mayn foter hot nisht gehat keyn breyre,

00:17:08.738 --> 00:17:12.431
zogt er, er iz shoyn gevezn yingl fun tsvontsik, vos, vet er im geyn haltn?

00:17:12.976 --> 00:17:24.108
zogt er, OKAY, az du farshteyst azoy, hot er gezogt, shoyn! ayngepakt, er hot im gegebn gelt, di mame hot zikh tseveynt, un azoy vayter, "geb akhtung", un azoy vayter, "se vet dir nisht zayn gut, du veystu, kum tsurik, un host a heym, du host ales, un du host fun alem gutn",

00:17:24.317 --> 00:17:27.483
OKAY. avek un nisht gekumen mer.

00:17:27.640 --> 00:17:30.842
me hot fun im gehert, eyn kartl hot er geshribn fun Rusland,

00:17:31.961 --> 00:17:34.976
UNK YASHOR, un dos iz es gevezn, alts iz ordenung.

00:17:35.758 --> 00:17:37.305
er iz geven farheyrat demolts?

00:17:36.973 --> 00:17:37.727
neyn.

00:17:37.850 --> 00:17:39.599
er iz geven, I MEAN, mir zenen gevezn,

00:17:39.723 --> 00:17:42.108
dray bridern vos zenen geblibn in der heym,

00:17:42.108 --> 00:17:44.072
vos fir zenen dokh geven farheyrat.

00:17:44.195 --> 00:17:46.957
iz gevezn YISRAEL, AVRAM, un ikh.

00:17:47.317 --> 00:17:50.011
un der iz avek. ikh bin geblibn mit AVRAM in der heym.

00:17:53.257 --> 00:17:55.597
un ir hot gehert fun im?

00:17:55.400 --> 00:17:57.453
mir hobn nisht gehert fun im gornisht.

00:17:58.438 --> 00:18:01.082
mir hobn fun im gornisht gehert bizkl nokh der milkhome.

00:18:04.766 --> 00:18:09.165
ven hot ir ongehoybn tsu filn a an enderung, a groyse enderung?

00:18:08.833 --> 00:18:12.439
di groyse enderung hob ikh hob ikh ongehoybn tsu filn shoyn in dos, in

00:18:12.883 --> 00:18:16.033
in di BEGINNING OF fertsikstn yor.

00:18:16.629 --> 00:18:26.512
in der BEGINNING OF fertsikstn yor bald, lomir zogn bald oyf yanuar, februar, hot zikh ongehoybn ongehoybn zikh azelkhe tsores, me hot aroysgenumen ale yidn tsu sharn shney, oyf di vegn.

00:18:26.754 --> 00:18:27.992
oyf di HIGHWAYS.

00:18:28.020 --> 00:18:31.997
me hot aroysgenumen yidn tsu dem, me hot shoyn ongehoybn tsu hakn iber di kep,

00:18:32.053 --> 00:18:34.134
me hot shoyn ongehoybn tsu shnaydn berd,

00:18:34.134 --> 00:18:35.771
me hot shoyn ongehoybn tsu rabeven,

00:18:35.771 --> 00:18:37.298
me hot shoyn ongehoybn tsu shlepn,

00:18:37.301 --> 00:18:39.644
mentshn hobn ongehoybn tsu bahaltn di skhoyres,

00:18:39.644 --> 00:18:43.185
mentshn hobn bahaltn di skhoyres in di kelern, me hot shoyn ongehoybn tsu trogn tsu bahaltn,

00:18:43.443 --> 00:18:49.355
un se hot zikh gemakht shoyn a panik, azelkhes un azelkhes, me hot gezen a daytsh do ze'mir gelofn oyf di ferte gas avek,

00:18:49.355 --> 00:18:52.486
me hot nisht gevolt onkukn keyn daytsh, me hot nisht gekent zen mer keyn daytsh.

00:18:52.486 --> 00:18:55.757
me hot nisht gekont, se gevezn, se hot zikh ongehoybn zikh khurbn!

00:18:55.982 --> 00:19:00.381
un der bruder hot gevust nebekh, er iz avek keyn Rusland, gezogt er blaybt nisht do, do vet zayn a khurbn.

00:19:01.061 --> 00:19:03.941
se hot ongefangen dos fertsikste yor zeyer biter.

00:19:03.997 --> 00:19:05.189
zeyer biter.

00:19:05.567 --> 00:19:08.160
zenen gekumen mer daytshn in ayer shtot?

00:19:07.828 --> 00:19:16.007
se gekumen mer daytshn, se gekumen mer militer, se gekumen mer GENDARMERIE, un di GENDARMERIE hot zikh bazetst bar undz in shtot in a groyse gebayde, zey hobn zikh gemakht UNK far zikh an eygn,

00:19:16.063 --> 00:19:18.954
a groyse hoyz, un zey hobn bazetst di shtot,

00:19:18.965 --> 00:19:23.836
un zey hobn badorfn arbetorers, un demolts hob ikh ongehoybn tsu arbetn, MOSTLY bay di GENDARMERIE.

00:19:24.163 --> 00:19:25.628
zey hobn mikh arayngenumen,

00:19:25.628 --> 00:19:28.561
zey hobn mikh lib gehat, ikh hob ongehoybn tsu redn mit zey daytsh gut,

00:19:29.073 --> 00:19:31.599
un ikh bin gevezn, veyst dokh, azoy, a yingl

00:19:31.925 --> 00:19:38.028
vos ikh bin geven sheyn ongetun, zoyber, un ales iz fayn, hobn zey mikh zeyer gern gehaltn, un ikh hob zey dertsu geredt oykh daytsh,

00:19:38.270 --> 00:19:39.986
fun vanet hot ir gekent daytsh?

00:19:39.654 --> 00:19:45.363
ikh hob azoy gekhapt shnel, bay in der BEGINNING mit zey, hob ikh ongehoybn tsu khapn zeyer shnel.

00:19:45.363 --> 00:19:48.997
un ikh hob zikh oysgelernt zikh eyns tsvey, un ikh hob geredt mit zey zeyer fayn daytsh.

00:19:49.307 --> 00:19:55.776
a fakt ikh red, ikh red gut daytsh, un ikh hob mit zey ongehoybn tsu redn, un ikh hob zikh UNK nokh un nokh tsayt, ikh hob azoy gearbet a yor tsayt,

00:19:55.787 --> 00:19:58.543
oyf zeyer postns, bay zey in ⟨posterunkes⟩.

00:19:58.554 --> 00:20:07.976
hob ikh gearbet un ikh hob geroymt, un vos hob ikh getun? ikh bin geven a shtubn-dinst. a shtubn-dinst heyst ikh hob gehakt koyln, ikh hob gehakt holts, ikh hob gemakht fayer, ikh hob geputst di shtivl zeyere,

00:20:07.976 --> 00:20:10.651
ikh hob geholfn dos, ikh hob geholfn dortn geshnaydt kartofl,

00:20:10.651 --> 00:20:13.958
vos me dortn alts badorfn, hob ikh gearbet bay zey, a shtubn-dinst.

00:20:13.978 --> 00:20:17.257
un dos iz geven far mir gut, ikh hob gehat a pas aheymtsugeyn,

00:20:17.302 --> 00:20:18.393
aroystsugeyn,

00:20:18.467 --> 00:20:20.211
ikh hob gekont geyn hin, ikh hob gekont aher,

00:20:20.211 --> 00:20:22.477
un dos iz bay mir gevezn gut, a yor tsayt.

00:20:24.474 --> 00:20:28.738
un un demolts di di aroysgeyn fun shtub iz geven bagrenetst?

00:20:28.811 --> 00:20:33.075
se geven, yo bagrenetst, nisht bagrenetst, se gevezn, vu me iz gegangen hot nisht getoygt.

00:20:33.485 --> 00:20:39.588
ze'mir aroysgegangen lomir zogn, tsum grenets, tsum mark arayn, mark iz dortn geven merstns dortn polyakn hobn gevoynt dortn, dortn hobn shoyn gevoynt mer polyakn,

00:20:39.746 --> 00:20:43.540
iz shoyn geven yo bagrenetst, vayl der polyak hot ongevizn, "dos iz a yid, dos iz a yid,"

00:20:43.540 --> 00:20:46.485
zogt men, "kum aher", me hot im tseshlogn, me hot im tseharget,

00:20:46.496 --> 00:20:47.587
di daytshn,

00:20:47.795 --> 00:20:52.261
iz geven bagrenetst, ober vi ikh bin aroysgegangen, vi zey hobn gevust az ikh bin a yid, hob ikh bay mir gehat a pshepustke,

00:20:52.605 --> 00:20:56.154
fun di GENDARMERIE, a pas, az me zol nisht mikh tshepen, ikh arbet far zey.

00:20:56.154 --> 00:20:59.484
az se hot mikh emetser tsugerufn, "HALT! vos vos makhstu HIER?"

00:20:59.692 --> 00:21:05.070
hob ikh im a vayz gegebn vos ikh makh, ikh gey tsu der arbet, do arbet ikh bay di POLICE, OKAY, gey, gey mir vayter.

00:21:06.172 --> 00:21:09.148
un di batsiung fun di nisht yidishe bafelkerung

00:21:09.176 --> 00:21:10.908
tsu di yidn in,

00:21:10.897 --> 00:21:13.051
iz gevezn zeyer bit- iz shoyn geven biter.

00:21:11.117 --> 00:21:12.276
in ayer shtot.

00:21:13.968 --> 00:21:16.477
vos umgefer hobn zey geton?

00:21:16.179 --> 00:21:20.223
zey hobn getun dos ales vos vos der, zey hobn getun dos vos di daytshn hobn getun.

00:21:20.398 --> 00:21:23.548
di daytshn hobn gehakt un gebrokhn, un getun, dos zelbe hobn zey getun.

00:21:24.144 --> 00:21:27.356
zey hobn oyf dem gevart, az zey zoln hobn a PARTNER, a koyekh,

00:21:27.356 --> 00:21:29.575
un vos der daytsh hot getun, hobn zey oykh getun.

00:21:29.561 --> 00:21:30.770
zey hobn geshosn?

00:21:30.664 --> 00:21:34.112
zey hobn nisht gekent shisn, zey hobn nisht gehat keyn gever. se genug zey hobn gehakt mit di hent.

00:21:34.607 --> 00:21:37.211
mit mit shtekenes, geshlogn,

00:21:37.211 --> 00:21:38.685
un ongevizn ver se a yid.

00:21:39.450 --> 00:21:41.672
un di daytshn hobn zey gelozt dos ton?

00:21:41.323 --> 00:21:42.229
yo.

00:21:42.572 --> 00:21:43.261
yo.

00:21:43.213 --> 00:21:45.772
zey hobn mitgear- zey hobn mit gearbet mit zey?

00:21:43.263 --> 00:21:44.405
di daytshn hobn...

00:21:44.867 --> 00:21:47.663
zey hobn, zikher hobn zey gearbet, di daytshn aleyn hobn dos gemakht.

00:21:47.887 --> 00:21:51.374
hobn zey dos oykh gemakht. di daytshn hobn gemakht, hobn zey oykh gemakht dos.

00:21:52.477 --> 00:21:55.824
un azoy zent ir geven oyf der fray, ir hot gekent

00:21:55.835 --> 00:21:58.394
voynen dortn in di zelbe hoyz vu ir hot gevoynt?

00:21:58.400 --> 00:22:03.575
mir hobn gekent, mir hobn gevoynt in dem zelbn hoyz. mir hobn nisht gedorfn ibergeyn, di geto iz geven dortn vu mir hobn gevoynt.

00:22:03.902 --> 00:22:07.831
oyb se gekumen a geto, shpeter iz gekumen der geto, iz geven der geto dortn in dem UNK,

00:22:06.922 --> 00:22:07.811
ven,

00:22:07.831 --> 00:22:11.084
in dem OBSZAR vu mir hobn gevoynt, iz geven der geto.

00:22:11.411 --> 00:22:13.273
ven hot zikh ongehoybn der geto, ven hot,

00:22:13.273 --> 00:22:16.720
ven hot men gemakht dem geto in in OPATOW?

00:22:14.752 --> 00:22:17.767
der geto hot men gemakht in tsvey, in tsvey un fertsikstn yor.

00:22:18.009 --> 00:22:20.467
ir gedenkt vos a monat, vos a date?

00:22:19.460 --> 00:22:22.931
ikh gedenk nisht dos vos iz gevezn, ikh bin avekgegangen eyn un fertsik.

00:22:23.848 --> 00:22:25.901
eyn un fertsiktn yor bin ikh shoyn nisht geven in der heym.

00:22:26.396 --> 00:22:30.356
iz der geto gevezn in OPATOW in tsvey un fertsikstn yor.

00:22:26.413 --> 00:22:27.268
der e-

00:22:29.805 --> 00:22:31.200
in tsvey un fertsikstn yor.

00:22:31.863 --> 00:22:35.080
un ir zent gevezn in OPATOW biz ven?

00:22:34.918 --> 00:22:37.393
biz eyn un fertsik, ende eyn un fertsik.

00:22:38.175 --> 00:22:40.414
bizkele nokh di yomtoyvim eyn un fertsik.

00:22:42.866 --> 00:22:45.105
biz nokh di yomtoyvim eyn un fertsik.

00:22:45.583 --> 00:22:47.062
UNK september.

00:22:47.355 --> 00:22:50.049
far vos zent ir avek? oder vi azoy zent ir avek?

00:22:48.722 --> 00:22:51.298
ikh bin ge- ot azoy. ikh bin avek,

00:22:51.388 --> 00:23:00.869
se geven azoy, mayn bruder hot gehat a UNK gesheft un er hot gehat, veyst dokh, er hot gehat di CONNECTION mit di GENDARMERIE, zey zenen arayngekumen nokh a ringl, arayngekumen nokh a zeygerl, arayngekumen nokh a dem un nokh a yents,

00:23:00.888 --> 00:23:04.109
a mol hot er geshenkt, a mol hot er zey farrokhtn, a mol hot er zey gegebn,

00:23:04.109 --> 00:23:13.120
azoy az zey hobn, zey hobn gehat zeyer groyse batsiungen mit mayn bruder, vos mayn bruder hot geholfn a sakh yidn aroysnemen fun di tfise, vos me hot zey arayngezetst, me hot zey badorfn geyn morgn shisn,

00:23:13.123 --> 00:23:15.710
un se gevezn a sakh vos mayn bruder hot zey bafrayt.

00:23:15.710 --> 00:23:21.386
un gelofn tsu di GENDARMERIE un er hot avekgegebn epes, flegt er bafrayndn der mentshn un azoy vayter, me iz gekumen, hot er bafrayt.

00:23:22.539 --> 00:23:24.558
iz gekumen a groyser S.S. man,

00:23:25.273 --> 00:23:28.204
arayn tsu mayn bruder in gesheft arayn, un er hot zikh mit im gut bakent,

00:23:28.428 --> 00:23:34.362
un er hot dortn gekoyft bayn im, a bisl gekoyft, a bisl gegebn far zayn froy a PRESENT, far di kinder a PRESENT,

00:23:34.655 --> 00:23:35.662
ANYWAYS,

00:23:36.748 --> 00:23:43.512
der mentsh hot gezogt er makht oyf in SANDOMIERZ in di Letsom, a ge- dortn a m- a CAMP,

00:23:43.512 --> 00:23:50.912
vos di mentshn veln hobn zeyer gut, zey veln arbetn nor far folksdoytshn, ir veyst far di folksdoytshn, tsuboyen, tsumakhn, reynikn, tun,

00:23:50.912 --> 00:24:00.620
"azoy", zogt er, "az me vet kenen dortn lebn". zogt er, "du host emetser vemen tsu shikn?" hot mayn bruder mir opgeshlogn dos gesheft, zogt er, "Pinekl, efsher voltstu avekgegangen", hot er gevust vos vart oyf mir.

00:24:00.930 --> 00:24:18.542
er hot gevust az mir veln zikh muzn tsesheydn, di shay- di daytshn hobn tsesheydt di mishpokhes. a kind do, a mame do, a a do, zogt er UNK efsher voltstu gegangen aroys dortn, un do host di gelegnheyt, der S.S. iz mayn's a guter guter FRIEND, a FRIEND, er kumt arayn, er ken zikh mit im gut, er nemt im aroys, er helft im.

00:24:18.632 --> 00:24:20.432
efsher voltstu gegangen mit im.

00:24:21.703 --> 00:24:27.823
hob ikh gezogt, OKAY. vos hob ikh gevust? mayn mame hot mir arayngepakt gelt do, ayngeneyt do, dortn, iberal a por dolar,

00:24:27.947 --> 00:24:29.986
un ikh hob mikh oyfgehoybn, ikh bin avekgeforn fun dortn.

00:24:29.986 --> 00:24:34.044
ikh bin avekgeforn un mer hot men fun mir nisht gevust, vu ikh bin, vu ikh gefin zikh.

00:24:34.044 --> 00:24:36.035
ikh bin geven draysik kilometer fun Apt,

00:24:36.035 --> 00:24:39.754
un gornisht getort shraybn, nisht getort visn vos ikh tu un vos ikh makh.

00:24:39.860 --> 00:24:41.592
vi alt zent ir geven demolts?

00:24:42.257 --> 00:24:44.175
demolts bin ikh shoyn alt geven draytsn yor.

00:24:45.834 --> 00:24:47.330
zent ir avek, avu?

00:24:47.538 --> 00:24:48.747
keyn SANDOMIERZ.

00:24:48.720 --> 00:24:50.503
vu shraybt zikh es SANDOMIERZ?

00:24:51.420 --> 00:24:58.721
S.A.N.D.O.M. I.E.R.Z. SANDOMIERZ

00:24:58.423 --> 00:25:00.476
un SANDOMIERZ iz gevezn,

00:25:00.093 --> 00:25:03.597
in dos SANDOMIERZ, dos heysn oyf oyf yidish Tsozomir.

00:25:04.042 --> 00:25:13.014
ober in SANDOMIERZ gufe, dos iz geven a bisl hinter di shtot, iz gevezn aza min Letsom hot dos geheysn, dos iz geven dortn a SCHOOL, Letsom.

00:25:13.408 --> 00:25:16.983
un dem L- Letsom hobn zey dos ibergenumen far undz.

00:25:16.983 --> 00:25:21.064
un far a CAMP tsu makhn. me hot fun dem Letsom gemakht a CAMP nor far yidn.

00:25:21.153 --> 00:25:25.276
a bisl SANDOMIERZer hot men genumen, a bisl apter yidn hot men genumen,

00:25:25.276 --> 00:25:29.360
di ale, di umgegnt vos me hot gekent hot men arayngenumen dortn a bisl yungvarg

00:25:29.360 --> 00:25:33.433
un me hot dos gemakht a CAMP un dortn iz geven di onfirershaft nor fun S.S.

00:25:33.236 --> 00:25:35.492
dos heyst an arbets-lager iz dos gevezn?

00:25:34.788 --> 00:25:36.009
an arbets-lager.

00:25:36.009 --> 00:25:37.714
ober der S.S. man,

00:25:37.742 --> 00:25:43.238
er iz geven der hoypt, er iz geven der shtub-onfirer, der firer fun dem lager, vos iz arayngekumen tsu mayn bruder.

00:25:43.445 --> 00:25:44.806
ir gedenkt zayn nomen?

00:25:44.762 --> 00:25:47.456
yo. zayn nomen iz gevezn BULION.

00:25:47.816 --> 00:25:55.894
BULION. B.U.L.I.O.N. BULION.

00:25:56.962 --> 00:25:59.100
zayn nomen gedenk ikh eybik

00:25:59.274 --> 00:26:06.271
vayl demolts ven me hot aroysgetribn di yidn in tsvey un fertsikstn yor, iz er gekumen mir zogn, "iz mer keyn JUDEN nisht DA in Apt NO MORE."

00:26:08.252 --> 00:26:13.208
demolts hot er mir dertseylt me hot ale yidn shoyn aroysgefirt, host shoyn nisht dem bruder, du host shoyn nisht keynem.

00:26:13.601 --> 00:26:15.047
ale hot men avekgefirt.

00:26:15.407 --> 00:26:18.793
un ir hot im nokh gezen shpeter oykhet, tsi neyn?

00:26:18.765 --> 00:26:20.059
vemen, dem BULION?

00:26:19.811 --> 00:26:20.463
yo.

00:26:22.089 --> 00:26:24.362
ven ikh hob gearbet dortn in dem lager,

00:26:26.347 --> 00:26:30.420
hot er mikh geflegt aheymnemen tsu zikh in shtub arayn, er hot gebrengt zayn FAMILY

00:26:31.202 --> 00:26:33.761
keyn SANDOMIERZ, di vayb mit tsvey kinder,

00:26:34.037 --> 00:26:38.621
un ikh bin gekumen arbetn far im in shtub oykhet, un bay im PRIVATE in zayn hoyz.

00:26:38.913 --> 00:26:41.304
vos a s- vos a sort arbet hot ir getun?

00:26:41.242 --> 00:26:44.395
bay im in hoyz hob ikh getun di zelbe vos ikh hob gearbet bay di GENDARMERIE.

00:26:44.395 --> 00:26:53.946
oykh gemakht dos zelbe, un geheytst, gevashn, gereynikt, geputst, ales gemakht, ales vos me darf. azoy vi a mentsh kumt arum in a shtub, azoy hob ikh gearbet bay im.

00:26:53.946 --> 00:26:58.899
un far nakht hob ikh aheymgeganen, er hot mir gegebn a pas fun im, er iz geven der hoypt, er iz geven dem

00:26:58.927 --> 00:27:01.891
er iz geven der hoypt fun dem firer fun dem lager.

00:27:03.112 --> 00:27:07.258
un ir hot gezogt az ir hot geton boy-arbet.

00:27:07.905 --> 00:27:11.173
boy-arbet hot men gearbet di firer bay folksdaytshn.

00:27:11.887 --> 00:27:16.221
bay di folksdaytshn, arum un arum hobn gevoynt folksdaytshn arum dortn der Latsom.

00:27:16.022 --> 00:27:16.742
un ir,

00:27:16.221 --> 00:27:17.467
oyf di derfer.

00:27:16.933 --> 00:27:19.020
un ir hot oykhet geton boy-arbet?

00:27:18.080 --> 00:27:19.678
un ikh hob gemakht boy-arbet.

00:27:19.633 --> 00:27:21.669
vos, vos a sort,

00:27:20.848 --> 00:27:33.110
vos me hot nor nisht badorfn, tsigl brengen, leym brengen, kaves makhn, ales vos me hot nor nisht badorfn hob ikh geholfn, se geven arbetorers vos ikh hob geholfn. a sakh zenen geven balmelokhes PROFESSIONAL. ikh bin nisht geven nokh keyn PROFESSIONAL.

00:27:33.453 --> 00:27:42.813
hob ikh geholfn yedn eynem vos eyner hot badorfn hob ikh geholfn, me darf hobn helfers oykhet. demolts hot men nisht geven lomir zogn MACHINERY, me zol oyfheybn di tsigl, brengt tsigl mit a UNK mit a, mit a vegele.

00:27:43.798 --> 00:27:45.649
tsigl, tsement.

00:27:45.806 --> 00:27:48.703
un kontakt mitn geto hot ir nisht gehat.

00:27:48.759 --> 00:27:50.745
keyn kontakt mitn geto hob ikh nisht gehat.

00:27:50.970 --> 00:27:52.652
in SANDOMIERZ iz geven a geto.

00:27:53.045 --> 00:27:54.182
ober in,

00:27:54.013 --> 00:27:56.904
in Apt hob ikh nisht gehat keyne kontakt nisht.

00:27:54.210 --> 00:27:55.335
in OPATOW.

00:27:57.078 --> 00:27:58.692
keyner hot nisht gevust vu ikh bin.

00:27:59.357 --> 00:28:01.984
un ir hot nisht gevust vos se tut zikh dortn,

00:28:02.259 --> 00:28:04.700
vu di eltern zenen, di brider, shvester.

00:28:03.305 --> 00:28:07.299
dos gornisht. ikh hob afile nisht gevust az me hot dem tatn maynem geshosn.

00:28:08.148 --> 00:28:11.062
dos vet men kumen shpeter vel ikh aykh zogn vi azoy ikh hob dos gevoyr gevorn.

00:28:13.768 --> 00:28:18.892
hot ir epes gekrign hilf fun di nisht yidisher aynvoyner dortn,

00:28:19.218 --> 00:28:20.478
arum dem lager?

00:28:20.670 --> 00:28:22.048
vos ikh hob bakumen hilf?

00:28:21.902 --> 00:28:22.571
ye.

00:28:22.357 --> 00:28:24.630
keyn hilf. gornisht.

00:28:23.893 --> 00:28:26.739
fun di, fun di poylishe aynvoyner?

00:28:26.272 --> 00:28:29.001
gornisht. keyn hilf.

00:28:30.153 --> 00:28:31.447
un in geto,

00:28:31.655 --> 00:28:37.741
fun OPATOW, hobn zey gehat dortn epes hilf funem fun di poylisher aynvoyner?

00:28:33.579 --> 00:28:34.350
yo.

00:28:37.190 --> 00:28:37.972
neyn.

00:28:37.972 --> 00:28:39.008
gornisht.

00:28:40.380 --> 00:28:42.096
nisht. gornisht.

00:28:43.063 --> 00:28:46.820
hot ir fun geto lebn in gantsn nisht gevust vos se tut zikh dortn.

00:28:45.797 --> 00:28:50.128
fun geto lebn nisht. mayn bruder iz gevezn, alts iz gevezn, ober ikh nisht, ikh bin nisht gevezn.

00:28:50.707 --> 00:28:52.507
ikh bin shoyn geven demolts in SANDOMIERZ.

00:28:52.952 --> 00:28:54.111
in Letsom.

00:28:54.740 --> 00:28:57.974
un vi lang zent ir geblibn demolts in Letsom?

00:28:58.335 --> 00:29:00.203
in Letsom bin ikh geblibn a yor.

00:29:01.625 --> 00:29:03.712
hot men gearbet alts bay di folksdaytshn

00:29:04.207 --> 00:29:06.761
un ikh hob gearbet oykh bay BULION, bay im in shtub,

00:29:06.789 --> 00:29:08.015
er hot mikh aheymgenumen,

00:29:08.122 --> 00:29:12.571
er hot mir gekent, hot er mikh aheymgenumen, ikh zol im dos tun, ikh zol akhtung gebn far di kinder.

00:29:13.100 --> 00:29:17.600
un di froy hot mikh gehandlt, afile ikh bin aheymgegangen in lager hot zi mir mitgegibt sendvitshn,

00:29:17.808 --> 00:29:18.849
zayn froy.

00:29:18.905 --> 00:29:22.359
un ven zi hot gekokht esn hot zi mir gegebn tsu esn eyder er iz nokh gekumen,

00:29:22.635 --> 00:29:26.241
hot zi mir gezogt mir, ikh zol nisht zogn ir man az zi hot mir gegebn far im.

00:29:26.465 --> 00:29:30.492
hot zi mikh ongezogt az az er vet mir fregn tsi ikh hob shoyn gegesn zol ikh zogn az nisht.

00:29:31.106 --> 00:29:32.754
vel ikh, vel ikh krign nokh a mol.

00:29:33.266 --> 00:29:36.787
un vifl mentshn zent ir gevezn in dem Letsom?

00:29:37.772 --> 00:29:40.140
in Letsom hot gekont zey ikh veys

00:29:40.151 --> 00:29:41.934
a tsvey, dray hundert mentshn.

00:29:43.239 --> 00:29:47.166
mir makhn an iberrays yetst, un mir veln tsubaytn di kasete.

00:29:46.597 --> 00:29:47.166
OKAY.
